products.title: ADATA USA Ultimate Su800 1TB 3D Nand 2.5 Inch SATA III Internal Solid State Drive (ASU800SS-1TT-C)
features: Dynamic SLC Caching and DRAM Cache Buffer for optimized performance
RAID Engine & Data Shaping for ultimate protection
products.description: Breathe new lives into your PCs simply by replacing existing conventional HDD or older generation SSD with ADATA ultimate SU880 internal SSD utilizing the latest 3d-nand flash chips for enhanced performance and reliability. Pcs with ADATA SU880 now boot-up in seconds comparing to minutes with conventional HDD. ADATA SU880 delivers read speed up to 560 MB/s and write speed up to 520MB/s through innovative intelligent dynamic-adaptive SLC NAND flash acceleration technology with integrated DRAM buffer, achieving significant performance improvement comparing to conventional HDD with read and write speed under 110 MB/s, all while consuming less than 1% of power comparing to HDD while in standby mode. Numerous advanced technologies were incorporated into ADATA SU800 to enhance the overall performance: RAID engine and data shaping support enhance overall drive stability and data integrity; LDPC error Code Correction minimizes possible error when writing data; DEVSLP feature to extend battery life and lower power consumption. ADATA SU800 works with all popular disk migration utilities, giving users more options. Bundled SSD toolbox utility gives user in-depth view of state of health of SSD, allowing fine tuning necessary to optimize drive performance and prolong overall service life. ADATA ultimate SU800 comes with a 3-year limited Warranty for worry-free ownership experience. Operating temperature 0 Degrees Celsius -70 Degrees Celsius and Storage temperature -40 Degrees Celsius -85 Degrees Celsius .
